 Knight: High attack, close combat hero. Ability to cause high damage to enemies and provide power BUFF for teammates
 Ranger: Remote combat hero, equipped with bow and arrow, ability to provide speed increase buff for teammates
 Mage: Healing hero, ability to brewing damage splash potion, ability to provide life regeneration buff for teammates;
